About This Company
Kendal & Co was established with the main aim to reformulate the standards of client relations within the Dubai real estate industry, through the utmost integrity and ambiguity. We strive to provide service of the highest quality, our ethical standards, straightforward dealings and open-book transparency is unparalleled.We instil a culture of innovation, discretion and foresight throughout the company and we strive to make the complex process of buying or selling a property in Dubai as simple as possible for our clients.
